<node ID="46ACD188-3B84-4B53-BC75-1276E81B8503" TEXT="chrome &#21319;&#32423;&#36328;&#22495;&#31574;&#30053;" COLOR="#344852" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FCB60D" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Chrome v80 </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>变化</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>在</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>月</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>4</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>日发布的新版</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Chrome 80</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>中默认值将为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Lax</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>。新版本对</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> cookie </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>模块安全策略提高了</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>sameSite </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>从</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>None </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>变成</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Lax, </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>其策略为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>、</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>post</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>、</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>ajax </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>对跨顶级域</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>(top-level navigations)</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>的请求不再携带其域名下自己的</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>cookie</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>了。</span></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>请求类型</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>示例</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	      SameSite=None </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（跨域）</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>SameSite=Lax </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（非同父域的跨域） </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>SameSite=Strict </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>（跨域）</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>链接</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	a href=&apos;&apos;	            </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Cookie	                      </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                    </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>预加载</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	link herf	            </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Cookie	                      </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                    </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>GET </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>表单</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> form method=&quot;GET&quot; </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Cookie	        </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                     </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>POST </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>表单</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> form method=&quot;POST&quot; </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Cookie	 </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                  </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe	iframe src=&quot;&quot;   </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Cookie	                     </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                  </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>ajax	$.get/post(&quot;...&quot;)	    </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Cookie	                     </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                  </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送  </span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>image	img src=&quot;...&quot;	   </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Cookie	                     </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>                                                  </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>不发送</span></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>对我们的影响如普惠工作台，</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>形式集成，且之前</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>内域名和外站域名不同，导致</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>内写入的</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>cookie </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>无法被下一次请求带去，登录无效，以及其他页面中跨域的</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>ajax</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>请求等。解决方式：</span></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>方式一：</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Chrome </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>中打开</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> chrome://flags/#same-site-by-default-cookies </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>和</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> chrome://flags/#cookies-without-same-site-must-be-secure </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，设置为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Disabled </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，重启浏览器，临时解决</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>方式二：外站域名由</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> puhui.didi.cn </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>修改为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> puhui.xiaojukeji.com </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>和</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>大多数</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>内的</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>xxx.xiaojukeji.com</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>一致，不跨父域即可</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>方式三：对仍有跨域需求的</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>ajax</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>、</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>iframe</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>等情况，需要将对于的跨域的域名接口升级为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>https, </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>然后</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>cookie secure: true, </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>然后才能将</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>cookie</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>强制设置为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> sameSite None </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>我们这三种方式分阶段都采取了，其中第三种方式，仅对</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>mis</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>系统有进行了设置</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>sameSite None </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>毕竟为了安全，</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2c </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>接口不会被请求伪造了</span></p></body>
</html>
